Step 1: Download the Installer
Click this link to download the official Windows installer for Python 3.12: Download Python 3.12 (64-bit Installer)
Step 2: Run the Installer (The Most Important Step)
1.	Double-click the file you just downloaded (python-3.12.x-amd64.exe).
2.	STOP! Look at the bottom of the installation window.
3.	CHECK THE BOX that says: "Add python.exe to PATH".
o	If you miss this, the command line won't work.
4.	Click Install Now.
Step 3: Install the Libraries
Once the setup says "Setup was successful," close it and open your Command Prompt.
Run this command to install the tools (Pandas, OR-Tools, xlwings):
https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.12.8/python-3.12.8-amd64.exe
py -3.12 -m pip install pandas ortools xlwings openpyxl
